snippet.title: LIKE A DRAGON: INFINITE WEALTH | Dondoko Island Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Too many street punks getting you down? Time for the getaway you deserve? Dondoko Island is the destination for you!

Create and manage the resort of your dreams in Like a Dragon: Infinite Wealth when it launches January, 26th 2024.

Pre-Order to get the Hero's Booster Pack & Special Job Set.
